<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{pageTitle}}</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">{{pageTitle}}</h1>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <h3>컬렉션 반복 처리 예제</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>문법 설명</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">배열이나 리스트의 각 요소를 반복하여 처리합니다.</p>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>문자열 리스트</h5>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        {{#fruits}}
                            <li class="list-group-item">{{.}} </li>
                        {{/fruits}}
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>숫자 리스트</h5>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        {{#numbers}}
                            <li class="list-group-item">번호: {{.}}</li>
                        {{/numbers}}
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h5>빈 리스트 처리</h5>
                    {{#emptyList}}
                        <ul class="list-group">
                            <li class="list-group-item">{{.}}</li>
                        </ul>
                    {{/emptyList}}

                    {{^emptyList}}
                        <div class="alert-alert-info">
                            <p>목록이 비어있습니다! </p>
                        </div>
                    {{/emptyList}}
                </div>
            </div>

            <h4>실제 사용 예시</h4>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>과일 목록 (카드 형태)</h5>
                    <div class="row">
                        {{#fruits}}
                            <div class="col-md-6 mb-2">
                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                                        <h6 class="card-title">{{.}}</h6>
                                        <small class="text-muted">신선한 과일</small>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        {{/fruits}}
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h5>번호 목록 (배지 형태)</h5>
                    <div class="p-3">
                        {{#numbers}}
                            <span class="badge bg-primary me-2 mb-2">Number {{.}}</span>
                        {{/numbers}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

            </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/mustache/inverted-sections" class="btn btn-secondary">이전</a>
        <a href="/mustache/partials" class="btn btn-primary">다음: 부분 템플릿 학습</a>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>